reviewText:
[...]

Don't pay $60 for a vhs tape.  Go to the link and watch it for free.  No reason to buy an old tape.

This video features Bill Moyers's interview of poets Donald Hall and Jane Kenyon.  It is a wonderful video offering insights into the personal lives and crafts of two of America's finest poets (before Jane Kenyon died in 1995).  But it's not worth $60.  Keep looking!
